description: The trail is a classic well used parks trail great views of the valley, can be a busy trail. About 9 one way.
directions: Parking is great , all 2 wheel drive access. Get to Enderby BC . Parking location  Lat 50.575928°  Long -119.104728°, Signs on the road off Hwy 97A through Enderby BC on Cliff Rd heading east then north on Brash Alen Rd.
title: Enderby Cliffs Trail
